acceptOwnership().details: The new owner accepts the ownership transfer.

balanceOf(address).details: Returns the total veMOE of the specified account.

returns.veMoe: The total veMOE of the account.

claim(uint256[]).details: Claims the pending rewards in bribe contracts for each pool in the pids list.

emergencyUnsetBribes(uint256[]).details: Emergency function to unset the bribes contract for each pool in the pids list, forfeiting the rewards.

getAlpha().details: Returns the alpha value, used to calculate the weight of a pool (weight = min(votes, votes^alpha)).

getBribesOf(address,uint256).details: Returns the bribes contract of a pool for an account. Will return address(0) if the account has not set a bribes contract for the pool.

returns._0: The bribes contract of the pool for the account.

getBribesTotalVotes(address,uint256).details: Returns the total votes of a pool for a bribe contract.

returns._0: The total votes of the pool for the bribe contract.

getMaxVeMoePerMoe().details: Returns the maximum veMOE per MOE.

getPendingRewards(address,uint256[]).details: Returns the pending rewards for an account for each pool in the pids list.

getTopPidsTotalVotes().details: Returns the total votes of the top pool IDs.

returns._0: The total votes of the top pool IDs.

getTotalVotes().details: Returns the total votes of all pools.

returns._0: The total votes of all pools.

getTotalVotesOf(address).details: Returns the total votes of an account for all pools.

returns._0: The total votes of the account for all pools.

getTotalWeight().details: Returns the total weight of all pools.

returns._0: The total weight of all pools.

getVotes(uint256).details: Returns the total votes of a pool.

returns._0: The total votes of the pool.

getVotesOf(address,uint256).details: Returns the votes of an account for a pool.

returns._0: The votes of the account for the pool.

getWeight(uint256).details: Returns the weight of a pool.

params.initialOwner: The initial owner of the contract.

isInTopPoolIds(uint256).details: Returns whether a pool ID is in the top pool IDs.

returns._0: Whether the pool ID is in the top pool IDs.

onModify(address,uint256,uint256,uint256.details: Called by the caller contract to update the veMOE of an account.

params.newBalance: The new balance of the account.
params.oldBalance: The old balance of the account.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pendingOwner().details: Returns the address of the pending owner.

setAlpha(uint256).details: Sets the alpha value, used to calculate the weight of a pool (weight = min(votes, votes^alpha)).

setBribes(uint256[],address[]).details: Sets the bribes contract for each pool in the pids list.

transferOwnership(address).details: Starts the ownership transfer of the contract to a new account. Replaces the pending transfer if there is one. Can only be called by the current owner.

vote(uint256[],int256[]).details: Votes for the pools in the pids list. Will update the top pool IDs in the MasterChef contract.
